               <p>The Prisoner deny'd the Fact, and call'd several Evidences present, whose Depositions made it appear more probable, that it dropp'd out of his Pocket, it being said to be shallow ; and that the Prisoner did not pull it out. He likewise call'd several Persons, who<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="173109080012"></xptr> gave him a good Character, upon which the Jury <rs id="t17310908-52-verdict256" type="verdictDescription">
